---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - davebeer.com">
	<main>
		<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="updated">Last updated: February 1, 2026</p>

		<section>
			<h2>Overview</h2>
			<p>
				This is a personal website and blog. I respect your privacy and am committed 
				to being transparent about any data practices.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Information Collection</h2>
			<p>
				This website does not collect personal information from visitors. There are 
				no user accounts, newsletter sign-ups, or contact forms that require you to 
				submit personal data.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Cookies</h2>
			<p>
				This website does not use cookies for tracking purposes. If any third-party 
				services are embedded (such as videos or social media widgets), they may set 
				their own cookies according to their respective privacy policies.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Analytics</h2>
			<p>
				This site may use basic analytics to understand general traffic patterns 
				(such as page views and referring sites). This data is aggregated and does 
				not personally identify individual visitors.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
			<p>
				This website may contain links to other sites. I am not responsible for 
				the privacy practices of external websites. I encourage you to review 
				their privacy policies when visiting them.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
			<p>
				I may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be 
				reflected on this page with an updated date.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>
				If you have any questions about this privacy policy, feel free to reach out.
			</p>
		</section>

		<p class="back-link"><a href="/">‚Üê Back to home</a></p>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 70ch;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.updated {
		color: #666;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	section {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	p {
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #333;
	}
	.back-link {
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}
	.back-link a {
		color: rgb(124, 58, 237);
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.back-link a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>
